OL,3,CAnger explodes on welfare with fears
OL,4,C100 MPs could oppose plans
OL,6,FThe best word to describe the mood
OL,7,Famong Labour MPs right now is despair.
OL,9,FAt behind-the-scenes meetings that
OL,10,Fhave been taking place in Parliament,
OL,11,Fanger at Keir Starmer and specific
OL,12,Fpolicies has spilled over in the wake
OL,13,Fof terrible election results.
OL,15,FThe fury (and an outspoken desire to
OL,16,Fbacktrack) over Winter Fuel Payments
OL,17,Fis well known.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
