OL,3,CAnger explodes on welfare with fears
OL,4,C100 MPs could oppose plans
OL,6,FThey simply hope that anger will
OL,7,Fdissipate.
OL,9,FOn Wednesday, I watched a debate led
OL,10,Fby Diane Abbott who warned that
OL,11,Freforms to PIP could become to
OL,12,FStarmer, what the poll tax had been
OL,13,Ffor Margaret Thatcher - her downfall.
OL,15,FIt was perhaps unsurprising to see the
OL,16,Fattack from her or other colleagues on
OL,17,Fthe left of the party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
