OL,3,CAnger explodes on welfare with fears
OL,4,C100 MPs could oppose plans
OL,6,FHer colleague, Tony Vaughan, now the
OL,7,FMP for Folkestone and Hythe said the
OL,8,FPM had set out the right "principle"
OL,9,Fto protect the most vulnerable but
OL,10,Fwarned that the policy so far failed
OL,11,Fto do that.
OL,13,FThe MP for South East Cornwall
OL,14,Fmentioned worried constituents. And
OL,15,Foutside the debate, Chris Webb, from
OL,16,FBlackpool South, told me some had
OL,17,Fturned up to his "surgeries" in tears.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
