OL,3,CAnger explodes on welfare with fears
OL,4,C100 MPs could oppose plans
OL,6,FWhen the party woke up to the
OL,7,Fdisastrous set of election results on
OL,8,FFriday, a number of MPs cited the
OL,9,FChancellor.
OL,11,FThe first Whatsapp read: "Well this is
OL,12,Fa f***ing mess...We need to sack some
OL,13,Fpeople," citing Reeves.
OL,15,FBut there is a challenge, as Labour is
OL,16,Flosing as many votes to the left as
OL,17,Fright.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
