OL,3,CAnger explodes on welfare with fears
OL,4,C100 MPs could oppose plans
OL,6,FThey argue that a voter who has just
OL,7,Fslipped from Labour to Reform and one
OL,8,Fto the Greens have more in common than
OL,9,Fyou might think - and are particularly
OL,10,Funited on the question of the cost of
OL,11,Fliving.
OL,13,FBut critics warn that the sheer
OL,14,Fbreadth of the coalition is too broad
OL,15,Fto make the task of uniting it easy.
OL,16,FVoters do seem united - however, in
OL,17,Fanger.
OL,19,FData we showed on the Peston show
OL,20,Frevealed that Winter fuel was both
OL,21,Fsalient and unpopular.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
